com.safenetinc.luna

Class LunaHAStatus

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.safenetinc.luna.LunaHAStatus

  • public class LunaHAStatus
extends Object
    Contains information about the current HA status. A LunaHAStatus object should be instantiated via the LunaHAStatus(int HAslot) constructor with the HA slot number to query. This object contains a vector of LunaMemberState objects which contain the actual status of individual members.
